OL,3,C'We need him close to us' - Care home
OL,4,Cclosure causes upset
OL,6,FA Knaresborough care home is closing,
OL,7,Fforcing residents to move further from
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,10,FSherburn House, run by the Wilf Ward
OL,11,FFamily Trust, cares for nine people
OL,12,Fwith learning and physical
OL,13,Fdisabilities.
OL,15,FRising costs and staffing issues have
OL,16,Fresulted in a planned closure on
OL,17,FTuesday 16 December. The closure was
OL,18,Ffirst announced in October, giving
OL,19,Ffamilies just over two months to find
OL,20,Falternative accommodation.
