OL,3,C'We need him close to us' - Care home
OL,4,Cclosure causes upset
OL,6,FDaniel Beardsley, was born with a
OL,7,Fchromosomal abnormality. He moved into
OL,8,Fthe purpose-built home a few months
OL,9,Fafter it opened in 2016.
OL,11,FOriginally his parents were told he
OL,12,Fwas unlikely to live past the age of
OL,13,Ffive, but now 27 - they're convinced
OL,14,Fthe support he's received has helped
OL,15,Fhim thrive.
OL,17,FDaniel's father Gavin Beardsley said:
OL,18,F"He's just proved everybody wrong.
OL,19,FEverything about him - he's just an
OL,20,Fabsolute warrior, an absolute fighter."
