OL,6,FNow Daniel has been moved to
OL,7,Faccommodation that's an hour from his
OL,8,Fparents.
OL,10,FGavin said: "We could potentially lose
OL,11,Fhim without being by his side. That's
OL,12,Four biggest fear now.
OL,14,F"He's lost his home, his friends, so
OL,15,Fwe need him close to us."
OL,17,FDaniel's mother Rebecca Fennell said
OL,18,Fthings could be missed by moving to a
OL,19,Fnew site.
