OL,6,FShe said: "Obviously because Dan's
OL,7,Fnonverbal, he communicates in his own
OL,8,Fspecial particular way. This is a
OL,9,Fskill that both Gav and I and the
OL,10,Fstaff at Sherburne, we've really kind
OL,11,Fof worked together as a team.
OL,13,F"So to then go to somewhere where it
OL,14,Fmight not even be picked up by
OL,15,Fsomebody because they might either not
OL,16,Fbe looking out for it or think it's
OL,17,Firrelevant - it's the exact opposite."
