OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Calendar, Wilf
OL,7,FWard Family Trust CEO Paul McCay said:
OL,8,F"We have given the required notice
OL,9,Fthat the local authorities expect from
OL,10,Fus. Regretfully, with a service such
OL,11,Fas this, that is only three months,
OL,12,Fand we worked with the local
OL,13,Fauthorities to make sure we understood
OL,14,Fhow we could do that safely, securely
OL,15,Fand well."
