OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Council corporate
OL,7,Fdirector for health and adult
OL,8,Fservices, Richard Webb, said: "We
OL,9,Falways want people to continue to live
OL,10,Fin their existing home where this is
OL,11,Fthe right decision for them and we are
OL,12,Fsorry to see that the Wilf Ward Family
OL,13,FTrust has made this decision about its
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,F"We support one resident currently
OL,17,Fliving at Sherburn House in
OL,18,FKnaresborough and we will work with
OL,19,Fthem to find a new home if this
OL,20,Fdecision goes ahead as proposed by the
OL,21,FWilf Ward Family Trust."
